text VictoryRoad_B1F_Text_SamuelIntro {
	"The thought that I'm getting closer to
	the POKéMON LEAGUE…

	I'm getting stage fright…"
}

text VictoryRoad_B1F_Text_SamuelDefeat {
	"I couldn't do a thing…"
}

text VictoryRoad_B1F_Text_SamuelPostBattle {
	"The POKéMON LEAGUE became distant
	again… What a letdown…"
}

text VictoryRoad_B1F_Text_ShannonIntro {
	"To win your way through the POKéMON
	LEAGUE, you need the trust of your
	POKéMON."
}

text VictoryRoad_B1F_Text_ShannonDefeat {
	"Your relationship is based on
	solid trust."
}

text VictoryRoad_B1F_Text_ShannonPostBattle {
	"By being together all the time, trust
	grows between POKéMON and TRAINERS."
}

text VictoryRoad_B1F_Text_MichelleIntro {
	"This isn't the goal. It's only a place
	on the way to the POKéMON LEAGUE."
}

text VictoryRoad_B1F_Text_MichelleDefeat {
	"That's the way!"
}

text VictoryRoad_B1F_Text_MichellePostBattle {
	"You'll do fine, for sure!
	Your POKéMON are all eager to go!"
}

text VictoryRoad_B1F_Text_MitchellIntro {
	"My POKéMON are cosmically
	awe inspiring!"
}

text VictoryRoad_B1F_Text_MitchellDefeat {
	"I've never met anyone like you before."
}

text VictoryRoad_B1F_Text_MitchellPostBattle {
	"Even outside of battle, I sense
	incredible power emanating from you
	and your POKéMON."
}

text VictoryRoad_B1F_Text_HalleIntro {
	"Okay, no need to get your back up!
	Relax, let's take it easy!"
}

text VictoryRoad_B1F_Text_HalleDefeat {
	"Whoa!
	Wonderful!"
}

text VictoryRoad_B1F_Text_HallePostBattle {
	"Sure, this is VICTORY ROAD.

	But it's not all that different from
	the path you've taken so far.

	Try to enjoy things the rest of
	the way!"
}
